{"tid":1800633,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知邊個tvb藝人係做官？","createTime":"2019-12-28T04:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T04:40:21.000Z","uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6e07301903ee6129f224849f4d5a754b6c905c8f","tid":1800633,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"係馬明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有生還者表示，客機出事前曾經激烈搖晃，撞到建築物後傳出巨響，機艙內一片漆黑，乘客要用手機照明。事故後，有近十名乘客協助救出其他被困的人。<br />\n<br />\n總統托卡耶夫主持內閣會議，將周六定為全國哀悼日；<span style=\"color: red;\">又委派總理馬明領導調查委員會，在下月10日提交初步調查報告。</span><br />\n<br />\n副總理斯克利亞爾表示，飛機起飛時機尾曾兩度觸及跑道，顯示起飛時已出現困難。當局已找到客機俗稱「黑盒」的飛行紀錄儀，將循人為或機件故障方向調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n笑死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8844e39cfbdc8a7cfd0b1a3c607271b363c9e18","tid":1800633,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"644a0ab33b49dbc06d7d816963380945398514e2","tid":1800633,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"08e7f5efcc7100b5f97f8051ff5aafa109a7a62e","tid":1800633,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:27:56.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"5a3d54b3ad94c9b35379841abce622710dd469c7","tid":1800633,"uid":129658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"陳國邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1861e17f93d4115bc0de1898c0dcd638c2b1fd47","tid":1800633,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2